```r
contrasts(hcc$pregnancy_stress) = c(0, 1) #none is baseline
hc_preg <- lmer(
  hc_trimlog ~ 
    seg_week * pregnancy_stress + 
    weeks_preg_cent + 
    (seg_week|ID), 
  data = hcc
)
summary(hc_preg)
```
